OL,3,C'Natalie has gone': Court told of
OL,4,Cphone call from murder accused to
OL,5,Cfriend
OL,7,FThe best friend of the man accused of
OL,8,Fmurdering Natalie McNally has
OL,9,Fdescribed how he phoned her screaming
OL,10,F"she's gone" on the night the 32-year-
OL,11,Fold was found dead.
OL,13,FStephen McCullagh of Woodland Gardens
OL,14,Fin Lisburn denies murder.
OL,16,FMs McNally was found strangled, beaten
OL,17,Fand stabbed to death in her Lurgan
OL,18,Fhome in December 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
