OL,3,C'Natalie has gone': Court told of
OL,4,Cphone call from murder accused to
OL,5,Cfriend
OL,7,FAnne McCullough told Belfast Crown
OL,8,FCourt the defendant phoned her "really
OL,9,Fupset". She told the court he "just
OL,10,Fkept screaming she's gone, she's gone,
OL,11,FNatalie has gone".
OL,13,FMs McCullough said he was "howling,
OL,14,Fcrying and screaming" and kept saying
OL,15,F"she's gone".
OL,17,FShe also told the court she still has
OL,18,Fnightmares about what the 36-year-old
OL,19,Faccused told her about how he found
OL,20,FNatalie's body.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
